  title="Sleeping with Lash Extensions | Best Practices | Orange County Guide"
  description="Learn how to sleep with lash extensions to maximize retention. Expert sleep tips from Orange County lash professionals."
  keywords="sleeping with lash extensions, lash retention, silk pillowcase, Orange County lashes"
